data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","content_index":0,"item_id":"msg_9d3b2a621a9814db00699fc627fb288190827663a36d5230bf","logprobs":[],"output_index":1,"sequence_number":238,"text":"**Smart Eyewear (Contoso Galaxy Innovations – SmartView Glasses)** is a wearable-glasses product category designed to combine everyday eyewear with hands-free computing, capture, and eye-protection capabilities .\n\n### Features\n- **Augmented Reality (AR) interface:** Displays an AR layer so you can view digital information in your field of vision .  \n- **Voice-controlled AI agent:** Lets you control functions and interact using voice commands for hands-free use .  \n- **HD video recording with 3D audio:** Records high-definition video while capturing spatial (3D) audio for more immersive playback .  \n- **UV protection + blue light filtering:** Provides lens protection against UV and helps reduce blue light exposure .  \n- **Wireless charging with extended battery life:** Supports cable-free charging and is designed to last longer per charge .  \n\nThe documentation also indicates the product has guidance for **fit/sizing, care & maintenance, a break-in period, safety tips, and troubleshooting**, suggesting it’s intended for regular daily use and includes support for common setup and usage scenarios ."}

